      "versionNonce": 679236295,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "从上图看，线程A和线程B之间要通信的话，必须经历以下两个步骤：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "6JRpqybxuclWOOJg2-m_u",
      "originalText": "从上图看，线程A和线程B之间要通信的话，必须经历以下两个步骤：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "V7soVvP4yaDx34DWOyA4G",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 247.096326755635,
      "y": 3013.5306785545745,
      "width": 532,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff4e6",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ST7-q0ycvIHsOheW5TOgE"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAPy",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 442369102,
      "version": 565,
      "versionNonce": 1782341929,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "7OI1b9aelus5yJwYiYh-w",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "7OI1b9aelus5yJwYiYh-w",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 252.43635361110375,
      "y": 3018.5306785545745,
      "width": 521.3199462890625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ST7-q0ycvIHsOheW5TOgE"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAPz",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 998808978,
      "version": 613,
      "versionNonce": 789864935,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1）线程A把本地内存A中更新过的共享变量刷新到主内存中",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "V7soVvP4yaDx34DWOyA4G",
      "originalText": "1）线程A把本地内存A中更新过的共享变量刷新到主内存中",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "uDPFiXQVqaOm4-O2ZQAjF",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 247.096326755635,
      "y": 3052.921700815062,
      "width": 531,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff4e6",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ST7-q0ycvIHsOheW5TOgE"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQ0",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 55672590,
