      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2）线程B到主内存中去读取线程A之前已更新过的共享变量",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "uDPFiXQVqaOm4-O2ZQAjF",
      "originalText": "2）线程B到主内存中去读取线程A之前已更新过的共享变量",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "o1gJ09R9AHucTZTYFlIp-",
