      "text": "JMM决定一个线程对共享变量的写入何时对另一个线程可见",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "5oHwU7OFhMCHgfqSI0vjb",
      "originalText": "JMM决定一个线程对共享变量的写入何时对另一个线程可见",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZUuR7kBW8NiI1bSAlxl5d",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 305.2300508459874,
