      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "RRZAfnbmFhP8goj6-tY4c",
      "originalText": "每个线程都有一个私有的本地内存，本地内存中存储了共享变量的副本",
