      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Java内存模型还规定了在执行上述八种基本操作时，必须满足如下规则：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "PQThAwJ9HVAZo7Bfvlyue",
      "originalText": "Java内存模型还规定了在执行上述八种基本操作时，必须满足如下规则：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wQkU8RiSeUs_AAy940FAs",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 181.5913776959094,
      "y": 4168.663207600559,
      "width": 903.3264641659352,
      "height": 85,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQg",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1897688210,
      "version": 169,
      "versionNonce": 740768873,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "DUz5dMz37t99GyHotHkGb",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "DUz5dMz37t99GyHotHkGb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 186.5913776959094,
      "y": 4173.663207600559,
      "width": 890.31982421875,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQh",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1851540878,
      "version": 281,
      "versionNonce": 2051529383,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 如果要把一个变量从主内存中复制到工作内存，就需要按顺序地执行read和load操作， 如果把变量\n从工作内存中同步回主内存中，就要按顺序地执行store和write操作。但Java内存模型只要求上述操作\n必须按顺序执行，而没有保证必须是连续执行。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "wQkU8RiSeUs_AAy940FAs",
      "originalText": "- 如果要把一个变量从主内存中复制到工作内存，就需要按顺序地执行read和load操作， 如果把变量从工作内存中同步回主内存中，就要按顺序地执行store和write操作。但Java内存模型只要求上述操作必须按顺序执行，而没有保证必须是连续执行。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "VSy61UMJOOpJQ_fvcmGn9",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 181.5913776959094,
      "y": 4258.306085475433,
      "width": 476,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
