      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "DqjwYQP7114UVRfyQRsgW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 186.5913776959094,
      "y": 4302.948963350309,
      "width": 891.7199096679688,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1310221262,
      "version": 280,
      "versionNonce": 1053859047,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 不允许一个线程丢弃它的最近assign的操作，即变量在工作内存中改变了之后必须同步到主内存中。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "4lU_VJ6WDr-HVXnH5fDW_",
      "originalText": "- 不允许一个线程丢弃它的最近assign的操作，即变量在工作内存中改变了之后必须同步到主内存中。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bFBfk01aGWi_ve59eN48c",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 181.5913776959094,
      "y": 4337.591841225183,
      "width": 847,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQm",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 255334482,
      "version": 123,
      "versionNonce": 1237403913,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "edR5QRi0tKIztGYhN7Gtf",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "edR5QRi0tKIztGYhN7Gtf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 186.5913776959094,
      "y": 4342.591841225183,
      "width": 831.7199096679688,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQn",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 149620754,
      "version": 328,
      "versionNonce": 614098951,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 不允许一个线程无原因地（没有发生过任何assign操作）把数据从工作内存同步回主内存中。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "bFBfk01aGWi_ve59eN48c",
      "originalText": "- 不允许一个线程无原因地（没有发生过任何assign操作）把数据从工作内存同步回主内存中。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Rw40BrdZUzM1TA-6VfLTN",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 181.5913776959094,
      "y": 4377.234719100059,
      "width": 903.3264641659354,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQo",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1627808146,
      "version": 136,
      "versionNonce": 1453670377,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "2DasdcYJareDl6vTyowRO",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "2DasdcYJareDl6vTyowRO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 186.5913776959094,
      "y": 4382.234719100059,
      "width": 891.2398681640625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQp",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 355908110,
      "version": 386,
      "versionNonce": 1094569767,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 一个新的变量只能在主内存中诞生，不允许在工作内存中直接使用一个未被初始化（load或assign）\n的变量。即就是对一个变量实施use和store操作之前，必须先执行过了assign和load操作。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Rw40BrdZUzM1TA-6VfLTN",
      "originalText": "- 一个新的变量只能在主内存中诞生，不允许在工作内存中直接使用一个未被初始化（load或assign）的变量。即就是对一个变量实施use和store操作之前，必须先执行过了assign和load操作。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "AuBSZdatzqSVzqvLAWC3x",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 181.5913776959094,
      "y": 4441.877596974933,
      "width": 903.3264641659352,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQq",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 483537618,
      "version": 199,
      "versionNonce": 1437031113,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "RJem6Ae72JOaH09mioOb6",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "RJem6Ae72JOaH09mioOb6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 186.5913776959094,
      "y": 4446.877596974933,
      "width": 891.7998046875,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 171193810,
      "version": 388,
      "versionNonce": 1059541575,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 一个变量在同一时刻只允许一条线程对其进行lock操作，但lock操作可以被同一条线程重复执行多\n次，多次执行lock后，只有执行相同次数的unlock操作，变量才会被解锁。lock和unlock必须成对出现",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "AuBSZdatzqSVzqvLAWC3x",
      "originalText": "- 一个变量在同一时刻只允许一条线程对其进行lock操作，但lock操作可以被同一条线程重复执行多次，多次执行lock后，只有执行相同次数的unlock操作，变量才会被解锁。lock和unlock必须成对出现",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "cE7t6k0n5kzrPKeOT-Wma",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 181.5913776959094,
      "y": 4506.520474849809,
      "width": 903.3264641659352,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQs",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 908626962,
      "version": 171,
      "versionNonce": 660806057,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "ky6aoysil6V65Y268WIAG",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "ky6aoysil6V65Y268WIAG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 186.5913776959094,
      "y": 4511.520474849809,
      "width": 890.3399658203125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 179325006,
      "version": 433,
      "versionNonce": 1194553703,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 如果对一个变量执行lock操作，将会清空工作内存中此变量的值，在执行引擎使用这个变量前需要重\n新执行load或assign操作初始化变量的值",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "cE7t6k0n5kzrPKeOT-Wma",
      "originalText": "- 如果对一个变量执行lock操作，将会清空工作内存中此变量的值，在执行引擎使用这个变量前需要重新执行load或assign操作初始化变量的值",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BBDTORi8FWTQfETr41jmp",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 181.5913776959094,
      "y": 4571.163352724683,
      "width": 903.3264641659352,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQu",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1337355602,
      "version": 175,
      "versionNonce": 218365065,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "MpqW0ei_n7IZ35PBJ6zVp",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "MpqW0ei_n7IZ35PBJ6zVp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 186.5913776959094,
      "y": 4576.163352724683,
      "width": 888.9798583984375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1838263186,
      "version": 430,
      "versionNonce": 850308231,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 如果一个变量事先没有被lock操作锁定，则不允许对它执行unlock操作；也不允许去unlock一个被其\n他线程锁定的变量。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "BBDTORi8FWTQfETr41jmp",
      "originalText": "- 如果一个变量事先没有被lock操作锁定，则不允许对它执行unlock操作；也不允许去unlock一个被其他线程锁定的变量。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aYpiuFYWD52RGhBQkxLzp",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 181.5913776959094,
      "y": 4635.806230599559,
      "width": 903.3264641659352,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQw",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 256431762,
      "version": 207,
      "versionNonce": 373654377,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "W1RV3Il7-XV-3MmQgF0Q5",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "W1RV3Il7-XV-3MmQgF0Q5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 186.5913776959094,
      "y": 4640.806230599559,
      "width": 845.3997802734375,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CG3im-CkDZ49Dl15Zx9TH",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 777916046,
      "version": 505,
      "versionNonce": 2102756263,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 对一个变量执行unlock操作之前，必须先把此变量同步到主内存中（执行store和write操作）。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "aYpiuFYWD52RGhBQkxLzp",
      "originalText": "- 对一个变量执行unlock操作之前，必须先把此变量同步到主内存中（执行store和write操作）。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "E9Pd5OKGl95nmOVd3aTYH",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 184.7357482659338,
      "y": 3295.4774287552887,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "nYLKgYJy9UDrlwaFLKmbB",
        "DYS8MxdyrXhAaGIRkgDrN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAQy",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
