      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775222525134,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "获取锁之前，线程会将共享变量的最新值从主内存中读取到线程本地的缓存中",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "hlQXSLoEK-vrwD9aw2M8-",
      "originalText": "获取锁之前，线程会将共享变量的最新值从主内存中读取到线程本地的缓存中",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
