      "crop": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ipvhmxfVUMrhIDYAE74Po",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1937.9031163329207,
      "y": 5162.844271406891,
      "width": 780.9197998046875,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Cw2hQMOK7kIFABGFyKuvy"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cATC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 375313490,
      "version": 346,
      "versionNonce": 1007442089,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "假设线程A执行到将singleton引用指向分配的内存地址这一步骤后，此时singleton已经\n不为null，但对象还未完成初始化。如果此时线程B执行到if (singleton == null)这一判\n断，由于singleton已经不为null，线程B会直接返回一个未初始化完成的singleton对象，\n从而导致程序出错。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "假设线程A执行到将singleton引用指向分配的内存地址这一步骤后，此时singleton已经不为null，但对象还未完成初始化。如果此时线程B执行到if (singleton == null)这一判断，由于singleton已经不为null，线程B会直接返回一个未初始化完成的singleton对象，从而导致程序出错。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
