      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "深入理解volatile禁止重排序的规则",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "9Do5JdlrUSy4PputsSDJt",
      "originalText": "深入理解volatile禁止重排序的规则",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3UvgFdvjNpOA3iXiDIajI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 321.9503638665759,
      "y": 8095.460993631471,
      "width": 1214.9836444392015,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fSOI4yYHhOl-RIFqlikkt"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cATO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1654926350,
      "version": 258,
      "versionNonce": 1381369321,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "案例：在Java多线程程序中，有时候需要采用延迟初始化来降低初始化类和创建对象的开销。双重检查锁定是常用的延迟初始化技术，但\n它有一个错误的用法。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "案例：在Java多线程程序中，有时候需要采用延迟初始化来降低初始化类和创建对象的开销。双重检查锁定是常用的延迟初始化技术，但它有一个错误的用法。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
