        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "DOaq9il-2oyBoyEl4yz-O",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 237.07090410832348,
      "y": 6962.88823640448,
      "width": 176.5799560546875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "O0VN_btwZJU4eMtOehD5b"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cATq",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 358176078,
      "version": 465,
      "versionNonce": 2020100649,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "lock前缀指令的作用",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "bxKpIA-M5ayXzqW-ntC6j",
      "originalText": "lock前缀指令的作用",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "JdOmaGWkuQSnHcDjnReTC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 232.43246364569154,
      "y": 7001.093698692621,
      "width": 1124.3816543907217,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "O0VN_btwZJU4eMtOehD5b"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cATr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 126611090,
      "version": 495,
      "versionNonce": 1488423143,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 确保后续指令执行的原子性。在Pentium及之前的处理器中，带有lock前缀的指令在执行期间会锁住总线，使得其它处理器暂\n时无法通过总线访问内存，很显然，这个开销很大。在新的处理器中，Intel使用缓存锁定来保证指令执行的原子性，缓存锁定将\n大大降低lock前缀指令的执行开销。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. 确保后续指令执行的原子性。在Pentium及之前的处理器中，带有lock前缀的指令在执行期间会锁住总线，使得其它处理器暂时无法通过总线访问内存，很显然，这个开销很大。在新的处理器中，Intel使用缓存锁定来保证指令执行的原子性，缓存锁定将大大降低lock前缀指令的执行开销。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QoM96q_mSHW-Xx3wA6xKT",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 232.43246364569154,
      "y": 7083.763637868293,
      "width": 838.3036081107658,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "O0VN_btwZJU4eMtOehD5b"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cATs",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2052946830,
      "version": 420,
      "versionNonce": 1460608265,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. LOCK前缀指令具有类似于内存屏障的功能，禁止该指令与前面和后面的读写指令重排序。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. LOCK前缀指令具有类似于内存屏障的功能，禁止该指令与前面和后面的读写指令重排序。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bKalQvuloHxtfAoHKz_IJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 231.3253590231975,
      "y": 7116.433577043965,
      "width": 1117.631325713023,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "O0VN_btwZJU4eMtOehD5b"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cATt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 16010322,
      "version": 464,
      "versionNonce": 985912327,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. LOCK前缀指令会等待它之前所有的指令完成、并且所有缓冲的写操作写回内存(也就是将store buffer中的内容写入内存)之后\n才开始执行，并且根据缓存一致性协议，刷新store buffer的操作会导致其他cache中的副本失效",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. LOCK前缀指令会等待它之前所有的指令完成、并且所有缓冲的写操作写回内存(也就是将store buffer中的内容写入内存)之后才开始执行，并且根据缓存一致性协议，刷新store buffer的操作会导致其他cache中的副本失效",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
