      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "JMM内存屏障插入策略",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "cqadQm5KS2_cj3jbrc6jE",
      "originalText": "JMM内存屏障插入策略",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Bn5fn5PY8l7tAP3wSlnz1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 234.92320535753447,
      "y": 5786.758769921153,
      "width": 1103.2334528977976,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RwKybnuJqLsM0mnDGcAC3",
        "O0VN_btwZJU4eMtOehD5b"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cATx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2040557138,
      "version": 361,
      "versionNonce": 1390788167,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "为了实现volatile的内存语义，编译器在生成字节码时，会在指令序列中插入内存屏障来禁止特定类型的处理器重排序。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "为了实现volatile的内存语义，编译器在生成字节码时，会在指令序列中插入内存屏障来禁止特定类型的处理器重排序。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zg3XgKe4Wx4cuMX3gmTL7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 238.24451922501635,
      "y": 5852.702106051491,
      "width": 485.4197692871094,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RwKybnuJqLsM0mnDGcAC3",
        "O0VN_btwZJU4eMtOehD5b"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cATy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1101125582,
      "version": 266,
      "versionNonce": 101805481,
