    },
    {
      "id": "D-hTxJueHeQgIZ_kFlE67",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 227.7447077210261,
      "y": 6295.0845264879645,
      "width": 997.6236624383098,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RwKybnuJqLsM0mnDGcAC3",
        "O0VN_btwZJU4eMtOehD5b"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAU4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1105992782,
      "version": 472,
      "versionNonce": 1163002441,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "由于不同的处理器有不同的松紧度的处理器内存模型，内存屏障的插入还可以根据具体的处理器内存模型继续优\n化。以x86处理器为例，x86不会对读-读、读-写、写-写操作做重排序，因此在x86处理器中会省略这3类操作对\n应的内存屏障，仅会对写-读操作做重排序。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "由于不同的处理器有不同的松紧度的处理器内存模型，内存屏障的插入还可以根据具体的处理器内存模型继续优化。以x86处理器为例，x86不会对读-读、读-写、写-写操作做重排序，因此在x86处理器中会省略这3类操作对应的内存屏障，仅会对写-读操作做重排序。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "4b0c5YCTlEQbAKc2N4pGQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 225.83886425389142,
      "y": 6378.442498347109,
      "width": 1121.034139760328,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RwKybnuJqLsM0mnDGcAC3",
        "O0VN_btwZJU4eMtOehD5b"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAU5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1546658766,
      "version": 464,
      "versionNonce": 1920787143,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "不同硬件实现内存屏障的方式不同，Java内存模型屏蔽了这种底层硬件平台的差异，由JVM来为不同的平台生成相应的机器码。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "不同硬件实现内存屏障的方式不同，Java内存模型屏蔽了这种底层硬件平台的差异，由JVM来为不同的平台生成相应的机器码。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
