      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "happens-before的定义",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "QP_jGhPUWkvxJqoldygjz",
      "originalText": "happens-before的定义",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BmmtqERn9fN5VhhRRQMtB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1488.2103846577397,
      "y": 5863.616727439632,
      "width": 985.4987477444548,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "LyzgWa1LOI3ZV5YZTqM9t"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAUF",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1306986386,
      "version": 376,
      "versionNonce": 546522727,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "JSR-133使用happens-before的概念来指定两个操作之间的执行顺序。由于这两个操作可以在一个线程之内，也\n可以在不同的线程之内。因此，JMM可以通过happens-before关系向程序员提供跨线程的内存可见性保证。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "JSR-133使用happens-before的概念来指定两个操作之间的执行顺序。由于这两个操作可以在一个线程之内，也可以在不同的线程之内。因此，JMM可以通过happens-before关系向程序员提供跨线程的内存可见性保证。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YCjmk6YVBSqtnlqy91b2R",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1489.1978774739646,
      "y": 5924.715885076712,
      "width": 440.49981689453125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "LyzgWa1LOI3ZV5YZTqM9t"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAUG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 765227662,
      "version": 373,
      "versionNonce": 1509422985,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "JSR-133规范对happens-before关系的定义如下：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "JSR-133规范对happens-before关系的定义如下：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZydOlUapwTM11hP4WSSBK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1485.9979142186853,
      "y": 5962.919686330397,
      "width": 1008.986720572122,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "LyzgWa1LOI3ZV5YZTqM9t"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAUH",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1585726802,
      "version": 405,
      "versionNonce": 1531699591,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1）如果一个操作happens-before 另一个操作，那么第一个操作的执行结果将对第二个操作可见，而且第一个操作\n的执行顺序排在第二个操作之前。  这是JMM对程序员的承诺， 注意，这只是JMM向程序员做出的保证。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1）如果一个操作happens-before 另一个操作，那么第一个操作的执行结果将对第二个操作可见，而且第一个操作的执行顺序排在第二个操作之前。  这是JMM对程序员的承诺， 注意，这只是JMM向程序员做出的保证。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2JAjZU5xqGA6qv0pU4Zaq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1485.107930087826,
      "y": 6015.977975736545,
      "width": 1004.4299490502495,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "LyzgWa1LOI3ZV5YZTqM9t"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAUI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1858793678,
      "version": 446,
      "versionNonce": 956440169,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2）两个操作之间存在happens-before关系，并不意味着Java平台的具体实现必须要按照happens-before关系指定\n的顺序来执行。如果重排序之后的执行结果，与按happens-before关系来执行的结果一致，那么这种排序并不非\n法，也就是说，JMM允许这种排序。这是JMM对编译器和处理器重排序的约束原则",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2）两个操作之间存在happens-before关系，并不意味着Java平台的具体实现必须要按照happens-before关系指定的顺序来执行。如果重排序之后的执行结果，与按happens-before关系来执行的结果一致，那么这种排序并不非法，也就是说，JMM允许这种排序。这是JMM对编译器和处理器重排序的约束原则",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ONaezg-ZN8QYfUHcT9G60",
      "type": "image",
      "x": 1513.9217347856072,
      "y": 6092.325779233264,
      "width": 496.394125217293,
      "height": 464.71852292406203,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "LyzgWa1LOI3ZV5YZTqM9t"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAUJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1356982030,
      "version": 495,
      "versionNonce": 1719933095,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775214283335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "status": "saved",
      "fileId": "dee93d7b51bcbd81c555c44f2561abceac98abb1",
      "scale": [
        1,
