      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "为了实现volatile的内存语义，JMM会限制编译器重排序，JMM针对编译器制定了volatile重排序规则表。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "nRWpMXpttAcNhc8mlO637",
      "originalText": "为了实现volatile的内存语义，JMM会限制编译器重排序，JMM针对编译器制定了volatile重排序规则表。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
