      "updated": 1775223494622,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3.  当第一个操作是volatile写，第二个操作是volatile读时，不能重排序。【连续volatile】",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "B4JQrUGL-RytNEh-OEI6L",
      "originalText": "3.  当第一个操作是volatile写，第二个操作是volatile读时，不能重排序。【连续volatile】",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZWGns06l0s6nTfPVo_2si",
